                  <handDesc>
                     <p>The left margin is 2.5 cm, upper margin 1.8 cm. The text is written in black ink on the front of a light-colored papyrus of rather fime texture. The single hand is large, broad and upright (letters 3 mm. high). Diacritical marks include one stop, one breathing mark, one trema and possibly a rough breathing mark</p>
